run(sql="

with cte as(
select a.orderDate as date, a.subOrderId, b.pogId from `temp.final_attri2` a left join `sinceLast75Days(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
where a.orderDate>='2023-03-29'
),

cte2 as(
select pogId from `temp.in_stock`
)

select cte.date, count(distinct cte.subOrderId) as Total_Orders, round(count(distinct case when cte2.pogId is not null then cte.subOrderId end)/count(distinct cte.subOrderId)*100,2) as Total_Feed_Coverage
from cte left join cte2 on cte.pogId=cte2.pogId group by cte.date order by cte.date

",1000)
